'''Ccix Nuredin''', isem-is n tidett, '''Nuredin Mezyan''', d agerruj n yedles azwaw/aqbayli: d amedyaz, d acennay, d asegbar (acteur) u d aɣeyyaḍ (Musicien). Ilul deg 1918 di taddart Agemun di Larba n At Yiraten. D mmis n Si Muḥand Taḥar Ugemun, i llan d asnelmad di taddart-is, deg aɣerbaz Sidi Abderaḥman. Imut deg 1999, yeǧǧad deffir-is timaḍ (d 100-yat) n izlan, d isefra akw d tuɣac. Afares-is (sa production) i bdat send/zdat (uqbel) n trad umdal amezwaru.

