== Talalit n Rradyu n teqbaylit ==

Deg 1938, Ccix Nuredin d netta i yellan deffir n tlalit n Rradyu n teqbaylit igellan di 'rue du Dr Saâdane (ex-Berthèzene)'. Tuɣal tin umi neqqar tura Amaṭṭaf wis 2 n Rradyu taɣelnayt n Lezzayer. Illa ixedem degs aṭas umezgun, rwayat 'sketč', akw d tuɣac d tedwilin. Rrayu aki, tella d ttin ansi id tefɣent tinazurin timuqranin, am : Lla Zina, Lla Yamina, Nna Crifa, Ǧamila, atg.

Ccix Nuredin isekles ugar n 500 tezlatin. Illa iḥemel azawan aɣerfan neɣ ayen umi neqqar 'Caɛbi'. Dɣa d netta i yuran unazzur n 'Caɛbi' Ḥaǧ Mrizeq, taɣuct ig ttwasnen imiren ilmen d tarbaɛt n takurt uḍar: 'Mouloudia d’Alger'. Illa i msuder (coyoyer) netta d inazuren imuqranen am : Ccix Lɛemqa, Muqran Agawa, d Sadeq Abǧawi, atg. Axedmen yakw tuɣac i Rradyu n teqbaylit i waken attidir. Daɣen Ccix Nuredin ixedem aṭas n tcequfin umezgun i Rradyu n Teqbaylit, anda i tturar d acḥal issegwasen tamtilt n yiwet n ṭmeṭṭut “Xalti Aduda”, zdat inazuren wiyaḍ am: Muḥamed Ḥilmi, Amar u Yaqub, Saɛid Zanun, Ali Abdun, Saɛid Ḥilmi, Aḥmed Aymen, atg.

Ccix Nuredin ixdem daɣen aṭas n tedwilin i rradyu n teqbaylit. Garrasent id yefɣen deg 1956, illan ilmend iccenayen deg ubrid ulemed neɣ 'Chanteurs amateurs'. Dɣa n nnuba yaki i yuɣalen ar zdat tettwasen s yisem : Icennayen uzeka.

== Ccix Nuredin d Sinima ==

Ccix Nuredin illa daɣen d asegbar (acteur) muqwren n Sinima. Amseḍru isura n Sinima i yettwasnen: Moḥamed Laxdar Ḥamina, iḥemel-it nezzeh. Dɣa ifek yas tamtilt deg usaru: 'Chronique des années de braise' ig bwin yiwen n warraz di 'Cannes' deg 1975. Di 1983, ifek yas daɣen tamtilt deg usaru : Tugna Tannegarut (La dernière image).

Ger isura wiyaḍ anda isɛa tamtilt, d wigi:

: 'Les hors-la-loi' n Tufik Fares deg 1968, 
: 'Patrouille à l’est' n Amar Laskri deg 1970,
: 'Tahia ya Didou' n Moḥamed Zinet deg 1973. 
: 'Elise ou la vraie vie' n 'Michel Drach' deg 1974, akw d 'Marie-José Nat' d Muḥamed Cwix
: 'El Chebka' n ɣwati Bendeduc deg 1976, 
: 'Chant d’automne' n Meziyan Yala deg 1982, akw d Rwiced d Ḥasan Lḥasani.

Llan daɣen sin usura 'Les Enfants de Novembre' d 'les Chevaux du soleil' ig ttwaxedmen di tmurt n Sbanyul akw ttnazurt n cnna taqbaylit Ḥnifa, ad fellas yilu isuref. Asaru yaki n 'les Chevaux du soleil' iḥekud tuddert n 'Lmuqrani', ar tura ur d yurar ara di Lezzayer.

== Timlilit d [[Sliman Σazem|'''Sliman Σazem''']] ==

Deg 1972 Ccix Nuredin yunag ar 'Paris' di Franṣa, anda yemlal d unazur [[Sliman Σazem|'''Sliman Σazem''']], u bdan amecwar n ccna di sin d acḥal isegwasen. Skelsen azal n 96 n tezlatin, garasent tid n teḍṣa d necraḥa. Dɣa d anecta iǧan deg 1981 Ccix Nuredin megdul seg umuɣ/amulas (Liste) n warazen ilmend n wid iqedcen i yedles azzayri.

